data.description: YOUR HOME AWAITS! Nestled at the end of a cul-de-sac this 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath features an updated kitchen w/ granite counter tops, ceramic tiling and an open concept to living room. Luxury vinyl plank on first floor, with an oversized gathering room on the lower level perfect for relaxing or a movie night! New carpeting in the 3 bedrooms with ample of space in the primary en suite! Relax from the hustle and bustle on your 1.3 acres just minutes from shopping and interstate access! Call to schedule your appointment today! **See Agent Remarks**
